<item>
            <title>[LU-444] Add LNetError for S_LND and S_LNET</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-444</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This changes the console error string for LND and LNET subsystem messages to LNet or LNetError depending on the severity. This should make it much easier to figure out where the issues are.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is from Oracle Bug 22502 att 32929.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
